    Title: The Wonders of the Holy Name
Tags:
  - Invocation=The Universal Elixir
---
This Divine Name is in truth a mine of riches, it is the fount of the highest
holiness and the secret of the greatest happiness that a man can hope to
enjoy on this Earth.
